    <div class="wpd-comment-text">
    <p>Wow, another huge chapter with a lot of fun tidbits and interesting info to unpack.</p>
<p>It’s nice to see Van and crew get a little of the recognition and acceptance that they deserve for once, rather than being shuffled out of the light or thrown out of the city.</p>
<p>The foreshadowing for Randolf was intriguing too, it’ll be interesting to see whether he’s going to be a potential ally or a boneheaded hater.</p>
<p>Thanks for the chapter!</p>

