    <p>Personally I thought the logical hoops Randolph had to jump through to arrive at the conclusion that Van had to be the demon king “core” was a bit flimsy and forced, but it does seem like they’re foreshadowing a potential confrontation there. Hopefully he does the smart thing and simply talks to Van instead of going after his life first.</p>

