    <div class="wpd-comment-text">
    <p>I’ll admit that figuring out Van has a Demon King Fragment is somewhat hard. I will say though a few things that have been established in the story thus far… First Dhamphirs are a rare race. It was discussed with Zod, but Vampires of the present day don’t see a need to have kids. Add in that the Pure Breeds actively hunt anyone who makes one for sport. The fact that Aldas faction reigns fairly high in the area it’s probably hard to even find a partner who would want to make a kid with a Vampire. This was also<span id="wpdiscuz-readmore-16653_16628"><span class="wpdiscuz-hellip">… </span><span class="wpdiscuz-readmore" title="Read more »">Read more »</span></span></p>
</div>
    <div class="wpd-comment-footer">
