    <p>The Divine Message is probably referring to the Divine Message Juliana received during her rebirth from Peria the Goddess of water alongside Perias Divine Protection.  Considering Peria is awake and healthy I don’t think the Goddess location is hers.</p>
<p>I think the Goddess location Peria gave is probably Botin’s.  Botin is still sealed and asleep.  Considering Van could break Aldas seal on Vida I think she wants Van to go and free Botin from her seal.  I think after that happens Peria will then jump ship.  Before Alda increases the guard around her and tries something extreme to wake her.</p>

