    <p>The problem with suspecting it to be the same damphir in both locations is there is not enough similarities between the incidents. Apart from involving a damphir that’s powerful both scenarios played out very differently if you were an outsider. In Hartner a damphir was going around the outskirt villages helping people and Orbia’s people. Here a damphir joined the commerce guild and tamer’s guild to sell meat skewers. Even if you are grant him the leap of logic that says these two damphirs must be the same person, then suggesting he must be the demon King’s main body because<span id="wpdiscuz-readmore-16609_16603"><span class="wpdiscuz-hellip">… </span><span class="wpdiscuz-readmore" title="Read more »">Read more »</span></span></p>
