    <p>Randolf is burnt out. As an elf he’s probably seen and experienced many things and come to the realization that he can’t help everyone. Now he’s going around paying off debts to people he knows or their descendants so that they don’t come looking for him anymore asking for more help. It sounds like he’s only looking to investigate Van to see if he might be a threat to his loved ones and begrudgingly the world too since he lives on it too after all.</p>

