    <p>Thanks for the chapter!</p>
<p>Little correction:<br/>
Zadiris, who had defeated monsters with spells even more advanced than those of the mages of the Mages’ Guild, and Zadiris, who had cut down the Giant that had been created by one of the bandits.</p>
<p>“and Zadiris, who had cut down”…etc… =&gt; Basdia, right?</p>
<p>Edit: Oh. Someone else already said it while I was still reading.^^</p>

</div><div class="wpd-comment-last-edited"><i class="far fa-edit"></i>Last edited 9 months ago by Darkhelios</div>
