    <p>The “Holy Mother” connection is a direct correlation. At around the same time that Darcia got the Holy Mother title, the denizens of Van’s empire were taught her (legitimately unbiased) gospel, and those that listened still took more issue with Heinz than she did, which got him that title. The Blue Flames group as a whole was very concerned when it popped up in the middle of their efforts in Bellwood’s Trial.</p>

